definitions.definition: A Semitic goddess of fertility , sexuality , and war , cognate in name, origin and function with the goddess Phoenician 𐤏𐤔𐤕𐤓𐤕 ( ʿAštart ) of Phoenicia.

main_definition: A Semitic goddess of fertility , sexuality , and war , cognate in name, origin and function with the goddess Phoenician 𐤏𐤔𐤕𐤓𐤕 ( ʿAštart ) of Phoenicia.
